      opts:['He ran faster than other forwards','His pressing shaped the entire opposition\'s build-up — by covering specific passing lanes and pressing at exactly the right trigger moments, he forced the opposition into the areas where Liverpool\'s midfielders could press and win the ball. His defensive work enabled the forwards to him to score','He only pressed when the team was losing','He pressed more than any other player in history'],
